379
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:36,600
This week, we'll be having pork soup

380
00:24:36,600 --> 00:24:37,800
while telling you
how we feel about pork soup.

381
00:24:37,800 --> 00:24:39,310
Thank you for the meal.

